                    "text": 387,
                    "type": 388
                },
                "When someone considers buying property in Phuket, their attention is usually focused on familiar factors: location, price per square meter, and the developer’s reputation. These aspects are indeed important, but here lies the biggest illusion — many investors believe that all the challenges end once the deal is closed.",
                "text",
                {
                    "type": 383,
                    "attrs": 390
                },
                {
                    "textAlign": 12
                },
                {
                    "type": 383,
                    "attrs": 392,
