                },
                {
                    "textAlign": 12
                },
                [
                    427
                ],
                {
                    "text": 428,
                    "type": 388
                },
                "Property in Phuket should not just exist — it must generate income and deliver on ROI expectations. Return on investment is not created at the moment of purchase; it is achieved once the property starts working and generating cash flow.",
                {
                    "type": 383,
                    "attrs": 430
                },
                {
                    "textAlign": 12
                },
                {
                    "type": 432,
                    "content": 433
                },
