                ],
                {
                    "text": 441,
                    "type": 388,
                    "marks": 442
                },
                "Without management",
                [
                    443
                ],
                {
                    "type": 400
                },
                {
                    "text": 445,
                    "type": 388
                },
                ", even the best projects can turn into a burden: low rental income, rising expenses, declining liquidity.",
